MIL-STD-1750A
Military Standard Sixteen-Bit Computer Instruction Set Architecture
4.1. Data Formats
4.1.1. Single Precision Fixed Point Data
Single precision 16-bit fixed point data shall be represented as a 16-bit 2's complement integer number with most significant bit (MSB) as the sign bit:
MSB                   LSB
-------------------------
|S|                     |
-------------------------
0 1                    15
4.1.2. Double Precision Fixed Point Data
Double precision 32-bit point data shall be represented as a 32-bit 2's complement integer number with the most significant bit (MSB) of the first word as the sign bit.

